College for Your World

Explore Our Classes

More Than Just a School

The Kentucky Community and Technical College System is much more than colleges and programs: we’re a community where you’ll find confidence, collaboration, compassion and success.

Whether you’re starting college for the first time or thinking about a career change, we’ve got you covered. Get started by finding the college and the program that works for you!

With flexible schedules, affordable tuition, and support services designed to help you succeed, we’re here to meet you where you are and help you get to where you want to be. Your journey starts here, and we’ll be with you every step of the way.

A Great Value

Afraid you can’t afford college? Well, you can. With the lowest tuition in Kentucky, financial aid options, and a helping hand to guide you through the process, we have you covered.

For the cost of one year at a university, you could go for two years here. That two-year degree can open up a new career, or complete the first half of your bachelor’s. Ready to learn more?
